name: Vital
headline: API for at-home health data
description: Vital is an API for at-home health data that makes it easy for health tech companies to collect data from 100's of wearable devices and deliver at-home test kits to their users. Healthtech companies need lab data as well as wearable data, and we give them access to both through a single line of code.

founders.name: Maitham Dib, Founder
founders.description: Love all things health-tech :) Previously applying ML in Aerospace, before joining Babylon health.

# One API, all health data.
Vital helps leading digital health & wellness companies connect to wearables and labs, through a single universal API.
[Get started](https://tryvital.io/<https:/app.tryvital.io/?id=1951ee59f53fd4-024ea14408c58e-57057e2e-9e340-1951ee59f54178c>)Book a Demo
![hero-grid](https://tryvital.io/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero-grid.webp&w=2048&q=75)
[Wearables![chevronIcon](https://tryvital.io/images/icons/arrows-right.svg)](https://tryvital.io/</wearables-api>)
![wearables-api](https://tryvital.io/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fwearables%2Fdevice-api.webp&w=3840&q=75)
[Labs![chevronIcon](https://tryvital.io/images/icons/arrows-right.svg)](https://tryvital.io/</labs>)
![lab-testing-api](https://tryvital.io/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero%2Flab-testing-api.webp&w=3840&q=75)
## The fastest growing health companies use Vital
![biowatch](https://tryvital.io/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcustomers%2Fageless.png&w=256&q=75)![biowatch](https://tryvital.io/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcustomers%2Fblokes.png&w=256&q=75)![lindus](https://tryvital.io/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcustomers%2Flindus.png&w=256&q=75)![parsley](https://tryvital.io/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcustomers%2Fparsley.png&w=256&q=75)![lifeforce](https://tryvital.io/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fcustomers%2Flifeforce.png&w=256&q=75)
## Personalized health data at your fingertips.
Gain a unified view into your health data from wearables and labs
Wearables Data
Pull in activity, sleep and workouts data from consumer grade wearables.
Medical Devices
Clinical grade data from blood pressure monitors, CGMs, BGMs and more.
Lab Tests
Blood, Urine, Saliva biomarker measurements collected across different modalities.
![wearable devices](https://tryvital.io/images/hero/wearables.webp)
## The widest coverage with one integration
Instantly access data from 500+ devices and results from labs across 50 States
## Integrate in hours not months
Save engineering hours, and use our API to pipe in data from hundreds of devices and labs in hours.
![phone-container](https://tryvital.io/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero%2Fphone.png&w=750&q=75)
![User dashboard](https://tryvital.io/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero%2Fuser-dash.webp&w=1080&q=75)
## Thousands of data sources
With over 500+ devices and labs supported, easily get the widest biomarker coverage.
[Full list of supported providers](https://tryvital.io/</wearables-api/supported>)
![connection](https://tryvital.io/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fhero%2Fwearable_connections.webp&w=1200&q=75)
## Simple Standardized Data
Pull in data from thousands of providers in structured JSON, or HL7 FHIR.
[Supported Data](https://tryvital.io/</wearables-api/supported>)
## Security from the offset
Vital is audited and certified against industry leading Third Party Standards.
[Security & Compliance](https://tryvital.io/</security>)

**Company Overview: Vital**

Founded in 2021 and part of the Y Combinator W20 batch, Vital is a London-based health-tech startup on a mission to revolutionize at-home health data collection. Their main offering? A simple API that allows health tech companies to seamlessly gather data from hundreds of wearable devices, alongside lab test results, all through a single line of code. With a compact team of ten, Vital is making a significant impact in the digital health landscape.

**Why Vital Matters**

Vital's API is built for efficiency and simplicity. Health tech companies often juggle multiple data streams to provide comprehensive health insights, which can be a cumbersome engineering task. Vital streamlines this by integrating wearables and lab data into one platform, reducing the time developers spend on integrations from months to mere hours. 

**Key Offerings:**

1. **Device API:** Effortlessly connect your app to wearable device data.
2. **Lab Test API:** Get streamlined lab testing across three modalities.
3. **Horizon AI:** Gain actionable insights by harnessing the power of AI on your health data.

They claim to support over 500 devices and labs, ensuring a wide coverage of health data without the hassle.

**Proven Value**

Vital's system isn't just beneficial in theory—companies using their API report concrete successes: 

- An increase of over 1,000 patients per month
- Rapid integration timelines, with some going from zero to fully operational in just three weeks
- Stunning cost savings, with companies reporting up to $450,000 saved in a year

Customers have praised Vital for exceptional functionality and support, illustrating a compelling partnership approach.

**Security and Compliance**

Vital prioritizes data security, with certifications like SOC 2 Type I, HIPAA, and GDPR compliance. This is essential in health tech, where data sensitivity is paramount.

**Final Thoughts**

In a world where health tech is rapidly evolving, Vital’s API acts as a bridge, connecting a multitude of health data sources with ease. By focusing on reducing engineering burdens while ensuring comprehensive health insights, Vital positions itself as a crucial ally for health tech companies striving to innovate in at-home health care. 

For more info, check out their website: [Vital](https://tryvital.io).
